metadata.description: This iconic collab between ICE and Knights of Degen bridges the gap between the web2 and web3 worlds like never before. This custom Game Time Pro features artwork unique to the Knights of Degen community, including each of The Roundtable Team and Advisor’s PFP’s as well as the Degen Tavern. ICE brings decades of expertise as a pioneer in the gaming industry in collaboration with Knights of Degen, the most prominent gaming community in web3, to make this one-of-a-kind work of art.
metadata.name: KOD Game Time Pro
